Entries.default: "Now you've done it. Think anyone will notice?"
"I say we bring the fist of the gods down on our enemies."
"I suggest we don't go back there any time soon."
"That takes me back to my childhood."
"Merla, I did not think the explosion would be quite that big."
"Magran's flaming tits, cap! The Sorcerer ain't never did nothing that fully fish-fucking mad!"
